(storylet: when $theme is "cinematic_noir" and $character is "Private Eye" and $setting is "Neon Bar" and $moment is "Whispered Name")

# Private Eye | Neon Bar | Whispered Name

Blue neon painted his face as she leaned in. Her lips barely moved—just enough to form the name that changed everything. The bar's din swallowed her whisper whole, but he'd caught it. Already his mind was reshuffling the case like a crooked dealer. That name. It connected dots he'd been blind to for weeks.

