(storylet: when $theme is "cinematic_noir" and $character is "Private Eye" and $setting is "Rain-Slicked Street" and $moment is "Final Glance")

# Private Eye | Rain-Slicked Street | Final Glance

Rain pounded the pavement like a judge's gavel. She turned—just once—her silhouette haloed by distant headlights. That look said everything his paycheck couldn't buy. Wipers kept time with his pulse as her taxi splashed into darkness. This wasn't an ending. In his line of work, there were only pauses between troubles.

